<paragraph blockId="141.[151,1437,151,2016]" pageId="141" pageNumber="142">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,541,151,176]" pageId="141" pageNumber="142">Slide-mounted adult female.</emphasis>
Body oval, probably quite convex in life. Anal cleft apparently not fused but with parallel margins, about 1/7th total body length. Length 3.5–4.0 mm, width 
<quantity box="[1036,1139,190,215]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.75" pageId="141" pageNumber="142" unit="mm" value="2.75">2.75 mm</quantity>
.
